entry.title: Stanadyne Fuel Manager Complete "Top Load" Assembly for GM 6.5L diesel engine with 5 micron element, 12V water sensor & 100 watt heater
entry.summary:
Vendor: Diesel Parts Canada
Type: Filtration
Price: 297.00

Stanadyne Fuel Manager Complete "Top Load" Assembly For GM 6.5L diesel engine with 5 micron element, 12V water sensor & 100 watt heater

All Fuel Manager units remove both particulates and water, and can be adapted for a variety of applications. Optional modular features can be added by the manufacturer, dealer, and in most cases the user.

Each employ Stanadyne's unique filtration process, trapping more impurities and water without impeding the flow rate. The product's design permits the replacement of elements without the use of tools and without spilling fuel, making service easy in the shop or in the field. When an element is replaced, an easily opened drain valve allows the filter to be completely and neatly emptied before it is removed.

Alternate number: 29367

Applications: Hummer, School Bus Chassis, P30, Blazer, C1500, C1500 Suburban, C2500, C2500 Suburban, C3500, Express 2500, Express 3500, K1500, K1500 Suburban, K2500, K2500 Suburban, K3500, Tahoe, G30, P3500, Savana 2500, Savana 3500, Yukon, G3500, H1

Type: Injectors

Certified Refurbished Injector forDodge Cummins 2003-2004.5 5.9L OE Common Rail 

Are you looking for a less expensive alternative to a Bosch remanufactured injector?

Are you in a bind or looking for a great deal on an injector?

Do you know how many injectors are replaced without being tested and diagnosed as failed?

We now offer a certified refurbished injector.
These injectors are tested on our Bosch EPS205 test stand to determine their current condition. 
The EPS205 checks the injectors for excessive leakage as well as how they perform during full load, pre-injection, part load and idle.
These injectors are NOT remanufactured they are tested and resealed injectors that have passed the stringent testing of the Bosch test equipment and meet the proper OE specifications.
Each injector comes with a copy of it's performance results and is covered by a 60 day replacement warranty. 
If your injector fails within the first 60 days we will supply you with a no charge replacement, no questions asked.
So if you're ready to take advantage of the savings on these tested good injectors place you order now!
